  <brief_title>Trial Comparing Two Techniques of Celiac Plexus Neurolysis for Treatment of Pain in Carcinoma Pancreas</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Trial Comparing Fluoroscopy Guided Percutaneous Technique Versus Endoscopic Ultrasound Guided Technique of Celiac Plexus Neurolysis for Treatment of Pain in Carcinoma Pancreas</official_title>
  <sponsors>
